Its fall and Halloween is just around the corner. Your at the store in New York search of a costume.
Your in the costume aisle when suddenly you head a loud scream. You look outside and see a women being
chased by a decomposed human almost like a, zombie? Behind them are 5 other zombies. Everyone runs out
the store racing towards their cars.

You need act fast before the zombies get to close.
1) Grab a fire extinguisher fight the zombies outside.
2) Run to your car and hope they dont catch you.
3) Hide on top of the shelfs and pray they dont find you.